價貴<br />\n上面話外國牛係外國食平其實好正常 不嬲個度出產多嘅嘢係個邊平係正常事黎<br />\n而且我係老美食個麥樂雞餐都要60港紙度 食漢堡包餐唔知 但一定貴過香港37.8喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於睇戲真係唔知 好耐無係香港睇過戲</blockquote><br />\n香港食野係平少少咁大把（其實都就追到外國水平），不過d位逼到乜，聽到哂對面枱講野，有d又限時坐60/90分鐘，又或者你未食完就趕撚住收你d碗碟，服務質素更加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求其講個外國例子，去美國唐人街整碗火車頭，都係講緊八九蚊美金度，服務又好有多料，牛肉又新鮮，又唔使俾人催住食，都不知幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a7d7ca4396813007acf8ef43827987ea638ba7","tid":292278,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:47:00.000Z","msg":"Oslo得46<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7594b6c5a6241a6303ef6faf8c6d6de64617e6","tid":292278,"uid":77731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:54:10.000Z","msg":"呢個咩機構？<br />\n香港機構淨係望到香港問題煲到變no.1"},{"pid":"99da0ac72888ad2a9446a8ee3c193cd31bd10d05","tid":292278,"uid":12634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:55:16.000Z","msg":"香港勁揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfdcff4f95a6b474cb0b26af31c9bd86b9c220e3","tid":292278,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:55:43.000Z","msg":"安哥拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9752e440d456d17fd87616b5ef794e44d06ed039","tid":292278,"uid":4661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:59:27.000Z","msg":"Mercer&rsquo;s 2017 Cost of Living Survey finds Asian and European cities &ndash; particularly Hong Kong (2), Tokyo (3), Zurich (4), and Singapore (5) &ndash; top the list of most expensive cities for expatriates. The costliest city, driven by cost of goods and security, is Luanda (1), the capital of Angola. Other cities appearing in the top 10 of Mercer&rsquo;s costliest cities for expatriates are Seoul (6), Geneva (7), Shanghai (8), New York City (9), and Bern (10). The world&rsquo;s least expensive cities for expatriates, according to Mercer&rsquo;s survey, are Tunis (209), Bishkek (208), and Skopje (206). <br />\n<br />\nMercer's authoritative survey is one of the world&rsquo;s most comprehensive, and is designed to help multinational companies and governments determine compensation allowances for their expatriate employees. New York is used as the base city and all cities are compared against it. Currency movements are measured against the US dollar. The survey includes over 400 cities across five continents and measures the comparative cost of more than 200 items in each location, including housing, transportation, food, clothing, household goods, and entertainment. <br />\n<br />\n份野係講緊外地工作者黎果個城市住既成本"},{"pid":"4e6b117a7576fca9ff394c4eb95caffb322c67f9","tid":292278,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a559796b88ed4c8a25356bd482e50943f7165826","tid":292278,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:14:21.000Z","msg":"幾時通縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722c23b45ea87189d6ca9209b46423bb1a1c8a04","tid":292278,"uid":57705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:15:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d3c0739d2508aaf4f34e543880460755581809b","tid":292278,"uid":43308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:15:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24477f8afdb8d61c98a2f275ff282eb503765fd5","tid":292278,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:19:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4762ea2fb16bb9c046273c44f64d560a2b8540c","tid":292278,"uid":55732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mercer&rsquo;s 2017 Cost of Living Survey finds Asian and European cities &ndash; particularly Hong Kong (2), Tokyo (3), Zurich (4), and Singapore (5) &ndash; top the list of most expensive cities for expatriates. The costliest city, driven by cost of goods and security, is Luanda (1), the capital of Angola. Other cities appearing in the top 10 of Mercer&rsquo;s costliest cities for expatriates are Seoul (6), Geneva (7), Shanghai (8), New York City (9), and Bern (10). The world&rsquo;s least expensive cities for expatriates, according to Mercer&rsquo;s survey, are Tunis (209), Bishkek (208), and Skopje (206). <br />\n<br />\nMercer's authoritative survey is one of the world&rsquo;s most comprehensive, and is designed to help multinational companies and governments determine compensation allowances for their expatriate employees. New York is used as the base city and all cities are compared against it. Currency movements are measured against the US dollar. The survey includes over 400 cities across five continents and measures the comparative cost of more than 200 items in each location, including housing, transportation, food, clothing, household goods, and entertainment. <br />\n<br />\n份野係講緊外地工作者黎果個城市住既成本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啦<br />\n如果唔係點會啲價差咁撚遠丫<br />\n<br />\n班expat又要住港島筆架山，食嘢睇戲去IFC圓方嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n仲唔貴過東京蘇黎世？"},{"pid":"5489e4e55000531f7839fb6bad1df1dacffbf961","tid":292278,"uid":57705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:23:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2bcc20eb0e663c78bf0617b16c8437e679f384ac","tid":292278,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:40:23.000Z","msg":"Shanghai Country China<br />\nHK country HK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3a0728cfa1eff03323294c3ff227a0465c8ef7","tid":292278,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:45:10.000Z","msg":"物價高唔係問題，問題係房地產佔大部分成本"},{"pid":"a9e696e8b82aed926306953328aa27a237b7a6bf","tid":292278,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:28:28.000Z","msg":"香港係貴過日本<br />\n但成日去上海 唔覺有咁貴"},{"pid":"edfa95b16dcedb30fafc955931d2d958dda360dd","tid":292278,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:28:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>竟然唔係挪威？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n Meanwhile, London (30), Aberdeen (146) and Birmingham (147) dropped thirteen, sixty-one and fifty-one spots respectively as a result of the pound weakening against the US dollar following the Brexit vote. Copenhagen (28) fell four places from 24 to 28. Oslo (46) is up thirteen spots from last year, while Paris fell eighteen places to rank 62.</blockquote><br />\n生活成本<br />\n人地高物價，但人工高"},{"pid":"25473de4718da23d341af58ffbb66e3fc613a16d","tid":292278,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:35:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mercer.com/newsroom/cost-of-living-2017.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mercer.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fcost-of-living-2017.html&d=JCnWpoNFTYXb1hSje%2B7cQIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=4342418e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mercer.com/newsroom/cost-of-living-2017.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercer_(consulting_firm)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMercer_%28consulting_firm%29&d=JCnWpoNFTYXb1hSje%2B7cQIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=907e281c\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercer_(consulting_firm)</a>"},{"pid":"c68900af4d6bb3ff09c64bb5a1bc838822e4ca33","tid":292278,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:41:35.000Z","msg":"食個all day breakfast $120<br />\n<br />\n真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"a4d755bb4a3a94b3dd2b212ea0b220a3e59a47bc","tid":292278,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"2012年既新聞已經有講過Luanda係好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLuanda係勁多外國石油公司係果到插旗，基本上D酒店乜乜柒柒都係做外國人生意，所以托到物價超高<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英國雜誌《經濟學人》今年選全球最高消費物價城市，挪威奧斯陸、法國巴黎和丹麥哥本哈根名列前三，香港打入20大。當人人以為非洲安哥拉（ Angola）戰亂貧窮，該國首都羅安達（ Luanda）的物價「貴到飛起」──在酒店客房點漢堡包，竟要約388港元，一房單位月租達約90,900港元，物價全球首屈一指。<br />\n安哥拉是非洲石油國，2002年內戰結束，經濟增長在全球數一數二，1,800萬人口中，1/3曾接受高等教育的人，其餘2/3蝸居貧民窟，在垃圾堆尋寶。貧富超懸殊，但經濟發展推高物價，迄今通脹率達13.5%，連在羅安達工作的外國人也叫物價貴。<br />\n<br />\n惟獨槍械較便宜<br />\n英製作人沃伊齊，前周入住商業區酒店 Epic Santa驚呼：「我知道這裏物價貴，但沒想到叫一個漢堡包，收費竟要32英鎊（388港元）。」酒店客房服務一向昂貴，但388港元一個漢堡包，仍比全球最貴的酒店客房公司三文治貴得多：今年5月的調查指全球26大城市中，最貴的酒店公司三文治在巴黎，也不過33.1美元（約258港元）。此外，羅安達一塊薄餅194港元，一對 Puma跑鞋2,242港元，一房單位月租7,500英鎊，惟獨槍械較便宜，一支 AK47步槍只需230港元。<br />\n23歲安哥拉人平托解釋物價飛升原因：「內戰時很荒蕪，和平後很多人仍捱餓，但也有人因石油賺大錢，他們買東西不看價錢。」也有人歸咎於安哥拉政府貪腐，自恃有價值153億英鎊（1,854億港元）的石油，只接受商務部承認的寡頭代理商入口。英國《星期日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n安哥拉部份物價<br />\n&bull;15粒車厘子　73港元<br />\n&bull;一磅番茄　89港元<br />\n&bull;薄餅　194港元<br />\n&bull; AK47自動步槍　230港元<br />\n&bull;雞尾酒 Martini　242港元<br />\n&bull;酒店房叫漢堡包　388港元<br />\n&bull;冒牌 Vans跑鞋　703港元<br />\n&bull; Puma跑鞋　2,242港元<br />\n&bull;油封鴨牛扒套餐　1,454港元<br />\n&bull;香檳　2,727港元<br />\n&bull;商業區酒店房價　3,515港元<br />\n&bull;健身室一年會籍　60,600港元<br />\n&bull;一房單位月租　90,900港元<br />\n資料來源：英國《星期日郵報》"},{"pid":"76cf6407fdd5a39a494d9c6b5da05f2d4866ae22","tid":292278,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:05:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04fddcf348664e68ed7f80946a80c04dceced0b4","tid":292278,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Mercer&rsquo;s 2017 Cost of Living Survey finds Asian and European cities &ndash; particularly Hong Kong (2), Tokyo (3), Zurich (4), and Singapore (5) &ndash; top the list of most expensive cities for expatriates. The costliest city, driven by cost of goods and security, is Luanda (1), the capital of Angola. Other cities appearing in the top 10 of Mercer&rsquo;s costliest cities for expatriates are Seoul (6), Geneva (7), Shanghai (8), New York City (9), and Bern (10). The world&rsquo;s least expensive cities for expatriates, according to Mercer&rsquo;s survey, are Tunis (209), Bishkek (208), and Skopje (206). <br />\n<br />\nMercer's authoritative survey is one of the world&rsquo;s most comprehensive, and is designed to help multinational companies and governments determine compensation allowances for their expatriate employees. New York is used as the base city and all cities are compared against it. Currency movements are measured against the US dollar. The survey includes over 400 cities across five continents and measures the comparative cost of more than 200 items in each location, including housing, transportation, food, clothing, household goods, and entertainment. <br />\n<br />\n份野係講緊外地工作者黎果個城市住既成本</blockquote><br />\n所以話華文傳媒真係好撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌佢老母 講撚到明&quot;for expatriates&quot;都可以skip咗唔寫, 亂尻咁報, 睇親華文新聞我都係「係咩? 聽住先, 信一半」, 之後得閒先google下國際大報點樣報</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知咩居心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7813ebdaec2c5e9a30a8658645e9adaa75aa42","tid":292278,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>羅安達一塊薄餅194港元，一對 Puma跑鞋2,242港元，一房單位月租7,500英鎊，惟獨槍械較便宜，一支 AK47步槍只需230港元。<br />\n<br />\n好明顯大家知道跟住會發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 